<paragraph blockId="1.[113,1089,1427,1622]" pageId="1" pageNumber="262">Body moderately stout, last visible tergite slanted about 20° from vertical. Integument light to dark reddish brown, antennae and four anterior legs testaceous, posterior legs reddish brown,</paragraph>
